### 2. **CC Workflow Studio (Late January 2026 - recent launch)**\nWhile launched just before February, this tool is highly relevant:\n- **Workflow-specific AI automation** for developers\n- Integrates Claude Code with workflow capabilities\n- Features include:\n  - Workflow templates for reusable processes\n  - AI optimization buttons for continuous workflow improvement\n  - Custom nodes for team-specific business logic\n  - Workflow-specific rules configuration in `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`\n\n### 3. **2026 AI Programming Assistant Landscape**\nMultiple sources highlight the trend toward **workflow-specific AI development tools** in 2026:\n- **End-to-end workflow automation** - from product requirements to deployment\n- **Intelligent milestone tracking** with automatic progress reporting\n- **Deep integration** with project management tools (Jira, Linear, Asana)\n- Multi-agent workflows for complex development scenarios\n\n## Notable Mention:\nThe search results indicate that **OpenAI was expected to launch** a visual AI workflow tool called \"AI Fabric\" at their Dev Day, though this appears to have been announced in late 2025 rather than February 2026.\n\nThe trend in early 2026 shows AI developer tools moving beyond general assistance to **workflow-specific automation** that integrates deeply into development pipelines and project management workflows.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
