 User experience evaluation\n   - A/B testing variant and prototype creation based on 200,000+ UX patterns\n\n3. **Base44** - Backend service for building AI agent applications, specifically optimized for Claude Code and Cursor. Deploy full-stack applications with a single command.\n\n4. **SuperX** - Comprehensive growth toolkit for X (Twitter) creators, ranked #1 in Product Hunt's February 2026 monthly rankings.\n\n5. **Supaboard AI** - AI business intelligence platform (champion of both daily and weekly rankings on February 5, 2026) that allows natural language queries for data analysis.\n\n## AI Tools for Debugging, Refactoring & Testing\n\n**Debugging Tools:**\n- **JamGPT** - AI debugging assistant with Chrome extension that provides automated bug analysis and intelligent fix suggestions\n- **Codegen** - AI assistant for Slack that analyzes, modifies, and improves codebases through natural language, creating production-ready pull requests\n\n**Development & Refactoring:**\n- Tools featuring automatic refactoring, debugging, and unit testing capabilities\n- Code completion, syntax highlighting, and refactoring features (Qt development tools)\n- AI-assisted coding with ChatGPT, GitHub Copilot, Ollama, and Aider integration\n\nThe search results indicate a strong trend toward **AI-powered developer tools** dominating Product Hunt rankings, with particular emphasis on:\n- Automated debugging and error resolution\n- Code refactoring assistance\n- Integration with popular development environments\n- Visual, no-code/low-code interfaces for AI-assisted development\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
