- Credit-based use of cloud-based AI assistance and the Junie coding agent\n- 30-day free trial of AI Pro access\n- Included with all JetBrains IDE licenses starting from version 2025.1\n\n**Paid Tiers:**\n- **AI Pro**: $10/month per user - includes higher usage quotas\n- **AI Ultimate**: $20/month per user - for demanding workflows\n\n**Junie AI Coding Agent:**\n- Now publicly available to all JetBrains customers\n- Compatible with IntelliJ IDEA Ultimate, PyCharm Pro, WebStorm, and GoLand\n- Support coming soon to PhpStorm, RustRover, and RubyMine\n\n**Additional Context:**\n- The free tier was introduced to compete with GitHub Copilot, Cursor, and other AI-driven IDEs\n- All Products Pack and dotUltimate subscriptions now include AI Pro\n- The system emphasizes privacy, security, and data control\n- Supports offline operation through Ollama or LM Studio for developers who don't want to upload code to the cloud\n\nThe search results show this was announced around April 16-17, 2025, not February 2026 as mentioned in your query. There may have been a confusion about the date.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
