h for new users\n\n### 3. **Qwen Code - The Terminal AI Agent**\n- Qwen Code is an **open-source AI agent for the terminal** optimized for Qwen models\n- It's a command-line tool that serves as a coding assistant\n- Helps developers rapidly convert ideas into code\n- Includes comprehensive documentation for users and developers\n- Supports tool development workflows and plugin extensions\n\n### 4. **Qwen3-Coder-Next** (February 4, 2026)\n- Released earlier in the month (February 4, 2026)\n- Specifically designed for coding agents and local development\n- Available with open weights under a permissive commercial license\n- 80B parameter model with 3B active parameters\n\n## Key Features of Qwen Code:\n- Terminal-based AI coding assistant\n- Optimized for Qwen models\n- Integration with popular development tools\n- Open-source with extension capabilities\n- Focus on rapid code generation and development workflow\n\nThe February 2026 releases represent a significant push by Alibaba into the AI-assisted coding space, with both model releases and developer-focused tools.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
