DE中无缝使用AI编码助手\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/gitblog_01188/article/details/141151070\"},{\"title\":\"如何在5分钟内快速上手Qwen Code：新手完整教程\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/gitblog_00009/article/details/137737903\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code\",\"url\":\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Qwen%2520Code/66293865\"},{\"title\":\"agentic terminal coding\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/itech/p/19274858\"},{\"title\":\"AI Coding 工具全盘点！从 IDE 到 Agent，新手到大神都能用\",\"url\":\"https://www.toutiao.com/a7573897119225168419/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Coding 新范式：基于 Spec Coding 的新玩法\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7564354270846894080\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code重大更新: 直接秒了GTP-5\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7553569648132407339\"},{\"title\":\"BNLNPPS/awesome-terminals-ai\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/BNLNPPS/awesome-terminals-ai\"}]\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Qwen Code\",\"url\":\"https://helpcdn.aliyun.com/document_detail/2974721.html\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen-Code\",\"url\":\"https://gitee.com/mirrors/Qwen-Code\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code技能系统终极指南：快速上手自定义技能\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/gitblog_01065/article/details/157085780\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code\",\"url\":\"https://m.oschina.net/p/qwen-code\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code VS Code集成教程：在IDE中无缝使用AI编码助手\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/gitblog_01188/article/details/141151070\"},{\"title\":\"Windows 下 AI工具配置（一）：Claude Code Router + Qwen\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/settingsun1225/article/details/154906453\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code重大更新: 直接秒了GTP-5\",\"url\":\"http://juejin.im/entry/7553569648132407339\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code 执行与部署\",\"url\":\"https://qwenlm.github.io/qwen-code-docs/zh/deployment/\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code v0.0.8 发布，深度集成 VS Code\",\"url\":\"https://m.oschina.net/news/368266\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen Code 免费用：每天 2000 次白给，我把 Claude Code 暂时放一边了\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/a7540265457429873186/\"}]\n\nBased on my search results, here's a comprehensive overview of **Qwen Code** - a terminal-based AI coding agent:\n\n## What is Qwen Code?\n\nQwen Code is a command-line AI programming assistant inspired by Gemini CLI, specifically designed and optimized for the **Qwen3-Coder** model series. It's developed by Alibaba's QwenLM team and serves as an AI coding agent that operates directly within your terminal.\n\n## Official Resources\n\n- **GitHub Repository**: https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code\n- **Documentation**: https://qwenlm.github.io/qwen-code-docs/zh/\n- **Gitee Mirror (China)**: https://gitee.com/mirrors/Qwen-Code\n\n## Key Features\n\n### 1. **Terminal-Native Experience**\n- Lives entirely in your terminal - no need to switch between IDE and browser\n- Native Terminal User Interface (TUI) that is responsive and themeable\n- Interactive Read-Eval-Print Loop (REPL) environment\n\n### 2. **Codebase Understanding**\n- Semantic-level editing of large codebases\n- Can explain entire project structures and dependencies\n- Generates dependency graphs for codebases\n- Understands unfamiliar systems and audits code for security/performance issues\n\n### 3. **Git Workflow Automation**\n- Automatically generates changelogs\n- Converts TODOs to GitHub issues\n- Analyzes commits grouped by feature\n- Handles Git operations without requiring scripts\n\n### 4. **Multi-Instance Support**\n- v0.5.0+ supports running up to 4 independent instances simultaneously\n- Multi-session capabilities for parallel task processing\n\n### 5. **Model Support**\n- Optimized for Qwen3-Coder models (qwen3.5-plus, qwen3-coder-plus)\n- Compatible with OpenAI SDK and various LLM providers\n- Supports ModelScope Provider\n\n### 6. **Multi-Language Support**\n- Built-in Chinese and English interfaces\n- Switch between languages using `/language` command\n- Custom language pack extensions supported\n\n### 7. **VS Code Integration**\n- Official VS Code plugin available (v0.5.0+)\n- Seamless integration with IDE development workflow\n\n### 8. **Developer SDK**\n- TypeScript SDK available for programmatic access\n- Java and Python SDKs planned for future release\n\n## Installation\n\n**Requirements**: Node.js v20 or higher\n\n```bash\n# Method 1: NPM installation (recommended)\nnpm install -g @qwen-code/qwen-code@latest\n\n# Method 2: Install from source\ngit clone https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code.git\ncd qwen-code\nnpm install\nnpm install -g .\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nStart Qwen Code by running:\n```bash\nqwen\n```\n\n### Example Commands:\n- \"Explain this codebase structure\"\n- \"Refactor this function\"\n- \"Generate unit tests for this module\"\n- \"What are the main services in this monorepo?\"\n- \"Describe the security model in this backend\"\n- \"Create a dependency graph for src/components\"\n- \"Analyze commits from the last week grouped by feature\"\n- \"Generate a changelog\"\n- \"Convert TODOs into GitHub issues\"\n\n## Authentication\n\nQwen Code offers multiple authentication methods:\n1. **Qwen OAuth** - Provides 2,000 free requests/day\n2. **OpenAI-compatible API** - Works with Alibaba Cloud DashScope\n3. Support for various LLM providers through ModelScope\n\n## Recent Versions & Updates\n\n- **v0.5.0** (Dec 2025): Multi-instance support, VS Code plugin, TypeScript SDK\n- **v0.3.0**: Stream JSON mode, three-layer Adapter architecture, session management\n- API rate limit: 60 requests/minute with no token limit (for certain plans)\n\n## Key Advantages\n\n- **Free usage**: Available through OpenRouter or ModelScope\n- **Better performance in large codebases** compared to Claude or GPT\n- **Zero switching cost**: Stays within your terminal workflow\n- **Cross-platform**: Supports Windows, macOS, and Linux\n- **Open source**: Apache 2.0 license\n\nQwen Code represents the growing trend of agentic terminal coding tools that provide autonomous code editing and execution capabilities directly from the command line, making it a powerful alternative to IDE-based AI assistants.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
